Code preview of 第三方保证信息关系表sl_third_ralation

drop table if exists sl_third_ralation;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: sl_third_ralation */
/*==============================================================*/
create table sl_third_ralation
(
thirdRalationId bigint(20) not null auto_increment,
projectId bigint(20),
customID bigint(20) not null comment '客户信息表id',
assureType smallint(6) not null comment '保证类型(企业1，个人2)',
primary key (thirdRalationId)
);

alter table sl_third_ralation comment '第三方保证信息关系表';

alter table sl_third_ralation add constraint FK_FK_THIRD_SMALL_REC foreign key (projectId)
references sl_smallloan_project (projectId) on delete restrict on update restrict;
